lots of students and lots of teachers and lots of people and it's great. Universities

756
00:42:51,624 --> 00:42:56,065
are usually deeply understaffed. We really need that. Do more than one class in a semester.

757
00:42:56,085 --> 00:42:57,005
Just make a package deal.

758
00:42:58,667 --> 00:43:03,629
I did a semester-long residency at Eastern Kentucky University.

759
00:43:03,889 --> 00:43:08,291
Got a full teacher's salary for the semester, got lots of benefits, did workshops, did all

760
00:43:08,311 --> 00:43:09,031
sorts of fun things.

761
00:43:09,151 --> 00:43:09,851
It was brilliant.

762
00:43:09,891 --> 00:43:11,572
And I got to be in a new place for a whole semester.

763
