00:44:31,737 --> 00:44:36,059
To help build the bridge, overlap the space, and share your unique experiences and perspective,

794
00:44:36,279 --> 00:44:38,080
the future of games is counting on you.

795
00:44:38,440 --> 00:44:39,260
So join us.

796
00:44:40,201 --> 00:44:44,283
Take a little break from the hustle and bustle before, you know, someone destroys education.

